@startuml loan-workflow-sequence
title Loan Application Workflow - Sequence Diagram

actor Client
participant "Loan Controller" as Controller
participant "Loan Workflow\n(VirtualObject)" as Workflow
participant "Credit Check\nService" as Credit
participant "Decision\nService" as Decision
participant "Contract\nService" as Contract

Client -> Controller : POST /api/loan/apply
activate Controller

Controller -> Workflow : processApplication(application)
activate Workflow

Workflow -> Workflow : Log: Start workflow

== Credit Check Phase ==
Workflow -> Credit : checkCredit(application)
activate Credit

alt Simulated Failure (30% chance, 1st attempt)
    Credit -> Credit : Fail with RuntimeException
    Credit --> Workflow : ❌ Exception
    Workflow -> Credit : Retry checkCredit
    Credit -> Credit : Calculate score\nbased on income/amount ratio
    Credit --> Workflow : ✅ CreditCheckResult\n(score, reportId)
else Success
    Credit -> Credit : Calculate score\nbased on income/amount ratio
    Credit --> Workflow : ✅ CreditCheckResult\n(score, reportId)
end
deactivate Credit

Workflow -> Workflow : Log: Credit check completed

== Decision Phase ==
Workflow -> Decision : makeDecision(application, score)
activate Decision

Decision -> Decision : Evaluate score:\n• >= 750 → APPROVED\n• 600-679 → MANUAL_REVIEW\n• else → REJECTED

Decision --> Workflow : Decision
deactivate Decision

Workflow -> Workflow : Log: Decision made

== Contract Generation (if Approved) ==
alt Decision = APPROVED
    Workflow -> Contract : generateContract(application)
    activate Contract

    Contract -> Contract : Generate contract ID\nwith timestamp
    Contract --> Workflow : ContractGenerationResult\n(contractId, timestamp)
    deactivate Contract

    Workflow --> Controller : LoanResult\n(APPROVED, score, contractId)
else Decision = REJECTED
    Workflow --> Controller : LoanResult\n(REJECTED, score)
else Decision = MANUAL_REVIEW
    Workflow --> Controller : LoanResult\n(MANUAL_REVIEW, score)
end

deactivate Workflow

Controller --> Client : HTTP 200 OK\nLoanResult JSON
deactivate Controller

note over Workflow
  **Restate Virtual Object:**
  • Durable execution
  • Automatic retries
  • State persistence per applicationId
end note

note over Credit, Contract
  **Restate Services:**
  • Stateless handlers
  • Automatic serialization
  • Observability
end note

@enduml
